I think because the lambda body is more than a single statement the return type is assumed to be void until c++14.  Adding `-> bool` to the lambda should remove the ambiguity. 

```c++
advCb = [](const ignition::msgs::Int32 &_req, ignition::msgs::Int32 &_rep) -> bool
{
   //...
```

